**Query #5**

    
    
    
    SELECT nome, email FROM adotante WHERE email LIKE '%gmail.com';

| nome          | email                  |
| ------------- | ---------------------- |
| Leon Baltazar | LeonBaltazar@gmail.com |
| Alice Chaves  | AliceChaves@gmail.com  |
| Melissa Leal  | Melissaleal@gmail.com  |

---
**Query #6**

    
    
    
    SELECT a.id_adocao, g.nome AS gato, ad.nome AS adotante, a.data_adocao
    FROM adocao a
    JOIN gato g ON a.id_gato = g.id_gato
    JOIN adotante ad ON a.id_adotante = ad.id_adotante
    ORDER BY a.data_adocao DESC;

| id_adocao | gato      | adotante      | data_adocao |
| --------- | --------- | ------------- | ----------- |
| 2         | Floquinho | Alice Chaves  | 2024-09-05  |
| 1         | Stive     | Leon Baltazar | 2024-08-10  |

